Phalanx Licensing Summary

This repository uses a split-license model:

1) Source code and generated schema artifacts are licensed under GNU GPL v3.0
   (or, at your option, any later version). See `LICENSE`.

2) Game/design media assets in `images/` and `resources/` are licensed under
   Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International
   (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0). See `LICENSE-ASSETS`.

3) The project name "Phalanx" and related branding are not licensed under the
   code or asset licenses. See `TRADEMARKS.md`.

If you are unsure which terms apply to a file, open an issue before reuse.
